{"tid":1462496,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[人手置頂] 梁天琦曾經講過","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T03:39:01.000Z","uid":95158,"like":89,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"17eb9a0140724886c3e9ec269ba82586c696059d","tid":1462496,"uid":95158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:41:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。</span><br />\n<br />\n一言堂塞鐵或者塞離境，我唔會反對你或者譴責你哋 兄弟爬山，各自努力，但希望大家組織行動前諗下天琦講過咩，各位抗爭者未來嘅行動都要諗下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">懇請大家不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，不要以自己寶貴的生命與當權者對賭，要時刻保持警覺與思考。</span><br />\n<br />\n義士流血我都好撚嬲，我都好仇視警犬，但請各位對準政權，五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰"},{"pid":"42ab32321a8db1bd93d73587786a8c33798eddaa","tid":1462496,"uid":95158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e7da97ec7408dea7f7bfd32b8a007526a70b45","tid":1462496,"uid":95158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957d434e59d96cd90fd8cc02aad604052827a030","tid":1462496,"uid":256741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6cb524d1edd4a890bfca4c3cd8398835c7ecc88","tid":1462496,"uid":95158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cec578c45bfa38d81fe1843ad3aa5346e435106","tid":1462496,"uid":95158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:50:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb13d5b8cd87b07a58f1577334844ab752059f3","tid":1462496,"uid":95158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi